keyMappings:
unmapAll

# Custom
map k scrollUp
map j scrollDown
map gg scrollToTop
map G scrollToBottom
map gi focusInput

map f LinkHints.activateMode
map H goBack
map L goForward
map R reload

map t createTab
map A removeTab

map a restoreTab
map T duplicateTab
map h previousTab
map l nextTab

map / enterFindMode
map v enterVisualMode
map n performFind
map N performBackwardsFind
map yy copyCurrentUrl

map o Vomnibar.activate
map b Vomnibar.activateBookmarks

# map ? showHelp
